Package: mtdesign
Type: Package
Title: Mander and Thompson Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Author: John Kirkpatrick <john.kirkpatrick@roche.com>
Maintainer: John Kirkpatrick <john.kirkpatrick@roche.com>
Description: Implements Mander & Thompson's (2010) methods for two-stage designs
    optimal under the alternative hypothesis for phase II [cancer] trials.  Also
    provides an implementation of Simon's (1989) original methodology and allows 
    exploration of the operating characteristics of sub-optimal designs.
